<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.5">
<l>pallāyi ravariv vūril piḷḷaikaḷ tīmaikaḷ ceyvār</l>
<l>ellāmuṉ mēlaṉṟip pōkā tempirā ṉīyiṅkē vārāy</l>
<l>nallārkaḷ veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāy ñāṉaccu ṭarēyuṉ mēṉi</l>
<l>collā ravāḻtti niṉṟēttic coppaṭak kāppiṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In this town there are many thousands of children</l>
<l rend="indent">doing mischief,</l>
<l>But none of them will be attributed</l>
<l rend="indent">[to anyone] but you, my lord. Come here!</l>
<l>You who stands in veḷḷaṟai where the good people [reside]!</l>
<l rend="indent">Light of Knowledge!</l>
<l>Come so that [I can] neatly fasten a Kāppu</l>
<l>while [I] am continually praising and blessing your body with words.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
